description:
It’s the Gee Thanks x Forever35 crossover episode you’ve been waiting—*checks notes*—two weeks for! Welcome to my producers and your favorite podcast hosts, Kate and Doree; Doree and Kate!


Doree’s item is a Kate recommendation, Kate’s product pick is something Caroline desperately needs, and Caroline’s choice makes her feel like the Very Organized Woman she really wishes she was.


Products in this episode:

  • Realistic LED Candles (Doree’s pick): https://amzn.to/34hgn0a 
  • Hydro Flask 32oz Tumblr (Kate’s pick): https://fave.co/36t0TYI
  • Hydro Flask 32oz Matching Lid (Kate’s pick): https://amzn.to/2PyFrum 
  • Tote Bag Insert (Caroline’s pick): https://amzn.to/2MLTbCX

Thanks for listening! Follow along with recs (and share your own via DM) on the “Gee Thanks, Just Bought It!” Instagram: www.instagram.com/geethanksjustboughtitpod

Check out all of the recommended products by past guests, listeners and Caroline herself at www.geethanksjustboughtit.com 

Shop the spreadsheet (updated with new recs all of the time!): https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1vdIkPMWhV0FlRux3u_DVpuGvakQxkF3EbYT2ZVv45B8/edit#gid=0

Want to get in touch more formally? Email: Caroline@geethanksjustboughtit.com

Subscribe to the Forever35 podcast: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/forever35/id1329229319

Follow Forever35 on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/forever35podcast

Follow Caroline on Twitter at www.twitter.com/carolinemoss
